we also offer afternoon tea with Prosecco. We also have a separate vegetarian afternoon tea menu and even a toddlers afternoon tea. Our toddlers afternoon tea is served with a soft drink and plenty of delicious but simpler sandwich and sweet treat choices. It’s the perfect way to spend time with family and friends.\r\n\r\nWe serve our brunch menu every day and we’re sure you will find something you love! We have all the classic brunch dishes from steak and eggs to full English and Shakshouka to Belgian waffles. We also have a selection of freshly prepared sandwiches served on a choice of either sourdough, ciabatta or bagel.</div>\r\n</div>'),(16562,212,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_content','field_5cff8c9fbfdd1'),(16563,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_large',''),(16564,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_large','field_5cff8ae74a8bf'),(16565,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_medium',''),(16566,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_medium','field_5cff8ae74a8c0'),(16567,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_small',''),(16568,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_small','field_5cff8ae74a8c1'),(16569,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_large',''),(16570,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_large','field_5cff8ae74a8bf'),(16571,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_medium',''),(16572,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_medium','field_5cff8ae74a8c0'),(16573,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_small',''),(16574,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_1_small','field_5cff8ae74a8c1'),(16575,212,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_switch','0'),(16576,212,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_switch','field_5cffb642d4431'),(16577,212,'layout_builder_4_multiple_images_switch','1'),(16578,212,'_layout_builder_4_multiple_images_switch','field_5cffb642d4431'),(16579,212,'layout_builder_5_panel_0_title','Book your table today.'),(16580,212,'_layout_builder_5_panel_0_title','fi