ives you a big, rounded peachy hit of fruit up front before coming together and delivering sweet nougat and hints of praline. Our roast on this coffee brings out its best aspects by taking its intrinsic sweetness and boosting its rounded mellow acidity to the forefront.'),(22062,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_1_content','field_5cff8c9fbfdd1'),(22063,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_large',''),(22064,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_large','field_5cd3ed7d6e3b0'),(22065,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_medium',''),(22066,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_medium','field_5cd3ed7d6e3b1'),(22067,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_small',''),(22068,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_image_small','field_5cd3ed7d6e3b2'),(22069,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_image',''),(22070,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_image','field_5cd3ed7d6e3ae'),(22071,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_title','Afternoon tea & brunch now being served.'),(22072,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_title','field_5cff8c9cbfdd0'),(22073,225,'layout_builder_2_panel_2_content','<div class=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"\" dir=\"ltr\">\r\n\r\nOur afternoon tea is served with a selection of freshly, hand-made and delicate finger sandwiches and sweet treats. All afternoon tea is served with a tea or coffee from our selection and for those celebrating we also offer afternoon tea with Prosecco. We also have a vegetarian and even a toddlers afternoon tea. It’s the perfect way to spend time with family and friends.\r\n\r\nWe serve our brunch menu every day and we’re sure you will find something you love! We have all the classic brunch dishes from steak and eggs to full English and Shakshouka to Belgian waffles.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),(22074,225,'_layout_builder_2_panel_2_content','field_5cff8c9fbfdd1'),(22075,225,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_large',''),(22076,225,'_layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_large','field_5cff8ae74a8bf'),(22077,225,'layout_builder_1_multiple_images_image_0_medium',''),(22078,225,'_